================================================================================
Third-party dependencies
================================================================================

`doc-rag` builds on the following open-source projects. Their respective
licenses apply to copies redistributed as part of this project (e.g. in
Docker images or deployment archives).

This list covers the project's declared dependencies and the optional
extras commonly installed alongside it. It is not exhaustive of
transitive dependencies — `pip show <package>` is authoritative for any
specific install.

Required runtime dependencies
-----------------------------

  numpy               — BSD-3-Clause
                        https://numpy.org/
  PyYAML              — MIT
                        https://pyyaml.org/
  PyPDF2              — BSD-3-Clause
                        https://github.com/py-pdf/PyPDF2
                        (Successor: pypdf, same license)
  filetype            — MIT
                        https://github.com/h2non/filetype.py
  python-docx         — MIT
                        https://github.com/python-openxml/python-docx
  tqdm                — MPL-2.0 AND MIT
                        https://github.com/tqdm/tqdm

